          <h3 class="sub-title">Myself</h3>
          <p class="align-left">Curiosity and an interest in technology drew me into the world of programming and development. I graduated from San Francisco State University with a Bachelor of Science Degree in Computer Science. I'm now a software engineer / full stack developer based in Los Angeles. I enjoy working in environments where I’m constantly needed and depended on. I am self-disciplined and always learning new things to get the job done.</p>

