          <%= image_tag "tech-logos/database.svg", class: "tech-logo" %>
          <%= image_tag "tech-logos/git.svg", class: "tech-logo" %>
          <p class="align-left">I'm adept with web development frameworks, particularly with <span class="emphasize">Ruby on Rails</span> and <span class="emphasize">Laravel</span>. I also have experience with front-end JS frameworks such as <span class="emphasize">React</span>, databases (<span class="emphasize">MySQL</span>, <span class="emphasize">PostgreSQL</span>, <span class="emphasize">SQLite</span>), and industry tools (<span class="emphasize">Git</span>, <span class="emphasize">AWS</span>, <span class="emphasize">Slack</span>, <span class="emphasize">Travis-Cl</span>, <span class="emphasize">Heroku</span>). Feel free to check out my <a href=<%= ENV['RESUME_LINK'] %> target="_blank">resume</a> for more.</p>

          <h3 class="sub-title">Interests</h3>
          <p class="align-left">I'm very passionate about anything that has to do with technology. My hobbies include being outdoors, watching and playing sports (mostly soccer and basketball), and reading up on anything tech. In my free time you'll probably find me playing video games, listening to new music, or taking a nap.</p>
